      "text": {
        "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Problem\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Problem</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Solution_1\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Solution 1</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Solution_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Solution 2</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_Also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See Also</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Problem\">Problem</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Problem\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Let <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/2/6/e/26eeb5258ca5099acf8fe96b2a1049c48c89a5e6.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"12\" height=\"10\" /> and <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/0/9/2/092e364e1d9d19ad5fffb0b46ef4cc7f2da02c1c.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$y$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"11\" height=\"13\" /> be positive reals such that <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/e/3/ee3c19c2097db41a478940611f5891c918bcdd59.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[x^3 + y^3 + (x + y)^3 + 30xy = 2000.\\]\" width=\"266\" height=\"19\" /> Show that <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/3/1/4/314a18c6b0fb2689e94987ee90b61b3fa94c755b.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x + y = 10$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"84\" height=\"16\" />.\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Solution_1\">Solution 1</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Solution 1\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After some manipulation we get:\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/e/7/1e79ddaca7390d2c910c62e8149266e8810432c6.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$3xy(10 - (x+y)) = 2((x+y)^3 - 10^3)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"297\" height=\"19\" />\n</p><p>Case 1: <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/4/5/14520ab03015c35a9ada23d407e7036436201209.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x+y &gt; 10:$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"93\" height=\"16\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/0/2/3/02319445b5a698225f20a0e387dee1efd5c539ff.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$RHS &gt; 0$\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px\" width=\"75\" height=\"13\" />, So <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/7/c/17c924be2d96aaeaadfdfd4b35b06d2a60edb5d9.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$LHS$\" width=\"41\" height=\"12\" /> has to be <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/b/9/1b98a367e7a3b900016ce23ba8ecaa33ce029c6a.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$&gt; 0$\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px\" width=\"27\" height=\"13\" />, so <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/f/6/2/f6233413a70e6b600fbfec97036f7e458f55c612.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$10 - (x+y) &gt; 0$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"129\" height=\"18\" /> or <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/3/c/d/3cdd8b7aec6b9556a58d8f836a6c8ce27a8a72e9.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x+y &lt; 10 =&gt; contradiction!$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"235\" height=\"16\" />\n</p><p>Case 2: <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/d/0/2/d0287230c427d250ebf30f95164aee719b3cb433.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x+y &lt; 10:$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"93\" height=\"16\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/7/5/a75505989676b7816c7a8f680ae9ba2f78229cbc.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$RHS &lt; 0$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"78\" height=\"15\" />, So <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/7/c/17c924be2d96aaeaadfdfd4b35b06d2a60edb5d9.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$LHS$\" width=\"41\" height=\"12\" /> has to be <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/3/1/a31e002bb10fa9452564aacac90861fa688882ab.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$&lt; 0$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"30\" height=\"15\" />, so <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/3/4/3/343aa1e1a5fbefdceb2dc8f173a6073cb1ee41a3.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$10 - (x+y) &lt; 0$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"129\" height=\"18\" /> or <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/d/7/9/d79368247982c8c21c13725b76812492529e0d97.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x+y &gt; 10 =&gt; contradiction!$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"235\" height=\"16\" />\n</p><p>Thus <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/3/1/4/314a18c6b0fb2689e94987ee90b61b3fa94c755b.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x + y = 10$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"84\" height=\"16\" />\n</p><p><br />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/b/8/ab8a050ca0f84a6aef15ead346438c2777533f30.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$Kris17$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"60\" height=\"14\" />\n</p><p>(This is wrong&#160;:|)\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Solution_2\">Solution 2</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Solution 2\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Rearranging the equation yields\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/d/d/8/dd8346c2a2209add7e910538837f42802cd63bae.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[x^3 + y^3 + (x + y)^3 + 30xy - 2000 = 0.\\]\" width=\"298\" height=\"19\" />\nIf <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/6/6/3/6631d7f1b7fd1489eb9406d34ae9566aa2a796db.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x+y=10$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"84\" height=\"16\" /> in the large equation, then <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/f/3/8/f38967c569a62f4c50e921f97b0944522672664a.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x+y-10$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"82\" height=\"16\" /> must be a <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/Factor\" title=\"Factor\">factor</a> of the large equation.  Note that we can rewrite the large equation as\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/9/b/2/9b2b6f6c62fa6dae97244c3dc3f0a4a90bef7102.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\begin{align*} 0 &amp;= (x+y)^3 - 1000 + x^3 + 3x^2y - 3x^2y + 3xy^2 - 3xy^2 + y^3 - 1000 + 30xy \\\\ &amp;= 2[(x+y)^3 - 1000] - 3x^2y - 3xy^2 + 30xy. \\end{align*}\" width=\"587\" height=\"47\" />\nWe can factor the difference of cubes in the first part and factor <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/3/c/1/3c1e2fb120953f946279e3807829929b390f8934.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$3xy$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"28\" height=\"16\" /> in the second part, resulting in\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/a/e/eae5403263b0190ad837a7a9eca2bcbf82659478.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\[0 = 2(x+y-10)((x+y)^2 + 10x + 10y + 100) - 3xy(x+y-10)\\]\" width=\"477\" height=\"19\" />\nFinally, we can factor by grouping, which results in\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/b/e/1/be19651eea4b36cfd3624775d4a58f7137edb1cc.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\begin{align*} 0 &amp;= (x+y-10)(2(x+y)^2 + 20x + 20y + 200 - 3xy) \\\\ &amp;= (x+y-10)(2x^2 + xy + 2y^2 + 20x + 20y + 200). \\end{align*}\" width=\"416\" height=\"47\" />\nBy the Zero Product Property, either <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/6/6/3/6631d7f1b7fd1489eb9406d34ae9566aa2a796db.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x+y=10$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"84\" height=\"16\" /> or <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/1/b/5/1b50065febbc693467696d03b66aac2c3b68dd24.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$2x^2 + xy + 2y^2 + 20x + 20y + 200 = 0.$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"304\" height=\"18\" />  However, since <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/2/6/e/26eeb5258ca5099acf8fe96b2a1049c48c89a5e6.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"12\" height=\"10\" /> and <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/0/9/2/092e364e1d9d19ad5fffb0b46ef4cc7f2da02c1c.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$y$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"11\" height=\"13\" /> are both positive, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/f/7/0/f708b273525ed6256ae0738470ad7e0071e472dd.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$2x^2 + xy + 2y^2 + 20x + 20y + 200$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"267\" height=\"18\" /> can not equal zero, so we have proved that <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/1/d/e1def0170458a3a61909f171092e60d1da2c257b.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$x+y = 10.$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"88\" height=\"16\" />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_Also\">See Also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2000_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: See Also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:95%; border:1px solid black; width:80%;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"background:#ccf;text-align:center;\" colspan=\"3\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_JBMO\" title=\"2000 JBMO\">2000 JBMO</a></b> (<b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_JBMO_Problems\" title=\"2000 JBMO Problems\">Problems</a></b> • <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://artofproblemsolving.com/community/c13_contests\">Resources</a>)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"50%\" align=\"center\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<br /><b>First Problem</b>\n</td>\n<td width=\"50%\" align=\"center\" rowspan=\"1\">Followed&#160;by<br /><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_JBMO_Problems/Problem_2\" title=\"2000 JBMO Problems/Problem 2\">Problem 2</a></b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">1</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_JBMO_Problems/Problem_2\" title=\"2000 JBMO Problems/Problem 2\">2</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_JBMO_Problems/Problem_3\" title=\"2000 JBMO Problems/Problem 3\">3</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2000_JBMO_Problems/Problem_4\" title=\"2000 JBMO Problems/Problem 4\">4</a> <b></b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/JBMO_Problems_and_Solutions,_with_authors\" title=\"JBMO Problems and Solutions, with authors\"> All JBMO Problems and Solutions</a></b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240908053223\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.035 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.038 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 328/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 839/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 839/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 43/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 6040/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    1.921      1 Template:JBMO_box\n100.00%    1.921      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki-wiki_:pcache:idhash:16670-0!canonical and timestamp 20240908053223 and revision id 217385\n -->\n"
